# 💡 One Improvement I'd Recommend

Instead of showing users a blank home screen after they sign up, show a friendly message like:

```
Welcome!

You haven't uploaded any blood reports yet.

Upload your first report
to begin tracking your health.

[ Upload My First Report ]
```

This guides first-time users and reduces confusion.

